        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="0">
            <title>SERVICE PROCEDURE</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove lens from the base by inserting a flat screwdriver into the slot at the rear of
                    the lamp. Twist the screwdriver to pop off lens.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install one gasket over lamp base, below lens retaining ring lip gasket to seal between
                    lens and base.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>Be sure gasket is not twisted.</para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Re-install lens by pressing it back onto the base. Lens should snap securely to the
                    base.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
